"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"clothing\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"public institutions\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And featherweight Rahimi, who has a first-round bye and will fight on 2 August as the first Muslim woman to box for Australia at the Olympics, sympathised with French athletes.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.9698503980991424, \"rank\": 0.03090561013699522, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}, {\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9203356048943856, \"rank\": 0.08643487888952928, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9565495740249931, \"rank\": 0.04514862947466701, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rahimi\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"2 August\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rights groups maintain the rules effectively discriminate against Muslims, although foreign athletes are not affected by the secularism rules.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1357, \"end\": 1364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.9649477522914941, \"rank\": 0.03473461072992558, \"text\": \"Muslims\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rights groups\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"foreign athletes\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the secularism rules\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's sad, with the French rules and that whole situation,\\\" Rahimi told Reuters.\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1455, \"end\": 1461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9565495740249931, \"rank\": 0.04514862947466701, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1507, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999999690772, \"rank\": 3.058735789542149e-11, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that whole situation\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"Rahimi\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I mean, as proud as I am to be here, I think in my heart I feel sad that I am able to be here with my hijab and the other French athletes and people are not.\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1639, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9565495740249931, \"rank\": 0.04514862947466701, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"my hijab\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still feel for the French athletes and I just hope that it can be overturned for them and they can participate and every woman can feel free in how they want to dress.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1698, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9565495740249931, \"rank\": 0.04514862947466701, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every woman\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It means a lot to me to be here as a representation of my faith, and to display to other women out there, in particular hijabi women, that they can participate in sport and feel welcome.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"a representation\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"my faith\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"other women\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"particular hijabi women\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that's really, really important.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what everyone wants to feel, they want to go somewhere and feel like they are included and they are not being discriminated against.\\\"\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response to Sylla's post, Amelia Oudea-Castera, minister for sport and the Olympic and Paralympic Games, had claimed the hosts were looking into a \\\"inventive\\\" solution.\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2250, \"end\": 2256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amelia_Peabody\", \"score\": 0.9978025781587521, \"rank\": 0.0022022607753876128, \"text\": \"Amelia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amelia_Peabody\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amelia_Peabody\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"Sylla's post\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"minister\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"the hosts\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"inventive\\\" solution\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our citizens expect us to follow these principles of secularism,\\\" Oudea-Castera said.. \\\"But we also need to be inventive about solutions to make everyone feel good,\\\" Amelia Oudea-Castera, minister for sport and the Olympic and Paralympic Games, said on Wednesday, adding that Sylla \\\"understands our principles, our rules\\\".\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our citizens\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"these principles\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"secularism\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"Oudea-Castera\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"solutions\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \",\\\" Amelia Oudea-Castera\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"minister\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2591}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2638}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"Sylla\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"our principles\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram